[==========================]
_Author: Victor Kolis Ford_
Version: 1.0.0
Game name: Snake

Rules:
1. Try to catch as many apples as possible in order to score the highest;
2. Hitting the borders would resolve to a game over;
3. Hitting yourself would resolve to a game over;
4. Use the arrow keys to control the snake;
5. Spacebar will pause/resume the game at your command.
